::Savanna::

She saw the ship.  It looked like a good ship.  She thought it was a 
shame that it was grounded like it was.  "Kluster, this is a proud 
looking ship.  It lookes like it has a few battle scars though.  I 
hope that you wil find the parts needed to get it operational again."

She was a bit impressed by the ship, but didn't want to show her 
feelings in front of bots that she had just met.
